title: Jake Carlisle snorted powder: Nine Network
text:
Jake Carlisle snorted powder: Nine Network   7:46   Jake Carlisle snorted powder: Nine Network 
The Nine Network has broadcast a video of what it alleges is St Kilda recruit Jake Carlisle snorting white powder. 
On the same day Carlisle was traded from Essendon to St Kilda, TV program A Current Affair broadcast a grainy clip in which a man appears to snort white powder. 
Nine allege the man is Carlisle, that he recently filmed himself, then sent the video to a friend via social media app Snapchat. 
It is unclear what the white powder in the video is.
